What a Bard CAN do is survive mez breaks MUCH better than a Chanter.  A) because we are not sitting on our arse when it breaks taking that max melee hit, and B) because we usuaully have better AC and definatly have more HP. <p><font size=2 face="Tempus Sans ITC, Verdana, Helvetica">
