</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udarksydodymoon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Darksyd Odymoon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 18<br> <font color=#CC9900>(1/30/01 1:26:29 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Bards on crowd control</span><hr size=1> I beg to differ on the enchanter only able to hold 3 mobs max. Back in the level 35-40 days I was able to keep 6-7 mobs mezzed if needed. If I didn't have tanks beating them down to reduce the number then no, I probably wouldn't be able to do it very long. <br>
